<body>
    <p><strong>Add / Edit Sites</strong></p>
<p>This screen will allow you to add a new Site or edit an existing Site</p>

<p>Select the Organization to which the Site belongs to</p>

<p>Enter the Site Name</p>

<p>Select the Location of the Site by clicking on the <img src="/img/map_marker.png" />. This will open up the Map. You need to click on the location and the selected Latitude and Longitude, Site Address.</p>

<p>Upload the Building Floor Map by clicking on the 'Select file' button and selecting the Image file. You can view the uploaded logo by clicking on the 'View Building Map' button. </p>

<p>Enter the Hub Details by entering the Hub Id, Hub Phone Number and click on the 'Add Hub Details'</p>

<p>Delete the Hub Details by clicking on the <i class='fa fa-minus-square'></i> icon</p>

<p>Select the Status of the User (Active / Deactive) and click on the Configure Sensors to save the Site details and navigate to the Sensor Configuration screen</p>

<p>To delete the Site select the Site and click on the Delete button</p>
</body>
</html>
